{
  "texts": [
    "All attention blocks were included in the Lora target modules.",
    "The training regimen for all DRG-LLaMA models were executed on a singular Nvidia RTX A6000 GPU with 48GB of graphics memory.",
    "As baseline models for benchmarking, we selected CAML 12, 13 and ClinicalBERT 15.",
    "CAML is an adjusted convolutional neural network (CNN).",
    "In CAML, clinical notes are tokenized and embedded with pre-trained word embeddings to form input representations."
  ]
}